title: Podman Container Diskstat
agents: linux
catalog: app/podman
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description: This check monitors the disk I/O statistics of a Podman container.
  More specifically, it reports the read and write IOs.
  It uses the `BlockInput` and `BlockOutput` fields reported by the Podman API.

item: The item will always be "SUMMARY".

discovery: One service is created.
